Cyberpunk style: A neon-lit digital envelope floating in a dark urban cyberspace, its surface fragmenting into geometric shards that transform into glowing data streams and holographic interface panels. The envelope hovers above a reflective wet street surface, with towering dark server monoliths in the background emitting soft purple and electric blue light. Small floating gadget-like cubes orbit the central envelope, each displaying abstract reactive patterns. The scene conveys transformation and hidden power within ordinary digital communication, with rain particles catching the neon glow and creating a moody atmosphere of technological evolution.
